&gt;&gt;&gt; I&#39;m pretty new to Heritrix 3 and despite my very good impression of the code and it&#39;s ability, I&#39;m having problems with a couple of things:
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; 1. How do I config the cxml file so I will crawl only in a specific domain, lets say http://example.com and only in sub domains of it?
