&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; https://webarchive.jira.com/wiki/display/Heritrix/FAQs
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; 2. How do i make the multiple queuing to work? does it happens automatically?
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; What do you mean by &quot;multiple queueing&quot;?
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; 3. I configed the cxml file so I wont process all the jpg/gif/png files but my logs still show me (Mimetypes) i process them.  this is what I did:
&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;bean class=&quot;org.archive.modules.deciderules.MatchesListRegexDecideRule&quot;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;             &lt;property name=&quot;decision&quot; value=&quot;REJECT&quot;/&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;        &lt;!--&lt;property name=&quot;listLogicalOr&quot; value=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;   --&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;        &lt;!--&lt;property name=&quot;regexList&quot;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;              &lt;list&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;                    &lt;value&gt;.*(?i)(&#92;.css(&#92;?.*)?)$&lt;/value&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;                    &lt;value&gt;.*(&#92;.bmp|&#92;.gif|&#92;.jpg|&#92;.png|bmp))$&lt;/value&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;              &lt;/list&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;             &lt;/property&gt;   --&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;       &lt;/bean&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; what is my mistake??
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; A definite problem is that your &#39;regexList&#39; property element is inside
&gt;&gt; XML comment markers -- &quot;&lt;!-- ... --&gt;&quot; -- so is not a part of the active
&gt;&gt; configuration.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; A possible problem could be the relative location of this rule with
&gt;&gt; respect to other scope rules; if this comes early, but then a later rule
&gt;&gt; ACCEPTs the same URIs, the later rule wins.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; You regexes also seem a bit suboptimal -- the CSS part could be mixed in
&gt;&gt; with the others, BMP doesn&#39;t need to be listed twice, you may want the
&gt;&gt; case-insensitive indicator for all suffixes, etc. -- but looks vaguely
&gt;&gt; functional for your purposes.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; - Gordon @ IA
